headline: EPAM (EPAM) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of digital engineering services company EPAM Systems (NYSE:EPAM) jumped 2.8% in the afternoon session after Wells Fargo boosted its price target on the stock to $247 from $185, while maintaining its positive "Overweight" rating.
